      <title>日本摩根士丹利资本国际 (MSCI) 权重领先中国升至五年高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/japan-s-weighting-hits-five-year-high-versus-china-on-asia-gauge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市的牛市使得该国相对于中国股市在亚洲基准指数中的权重升至 2018 年底的水平，突显出投资者在两个巨大市场之间的偏好发生了转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/japan-s-weighting-hits-five-year-high-versus-china-on-asia-gauge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
